<section class="section section--border-top wrap">
  <h2 class="section-label">How I Work</h2>
  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Bridge, don't translate</h3>
      <p class="small">I don't translate between engineering and the business. I sit in both rooms
      well enough that translation isn't necessary.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Governance as infrastructure</h3>
      <p class="small">Compliance and ethics review, built into the pipeline from day one. It ships
      faster than bolting it on after legal finds the problem.</p>
